@startuml
title Agentic Flow v2.0.0 - Actual Run Flow

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Team Lead" as TL
participant "Product Manager" as PM
participant "Java Architect" as ARCH
participant "Reviewer" as REV
participant "Java Coder" as CODER

note over TL,CODER #E2E8F0
Green = passed gate
Yellow = rejected / returned / degraded state
Red = red card
end note

group Planning Phase
TL -> PM : Create story
PM -[#22C55E]> TL : Story returned and accepted

TL -> ARCH : Create plan
ARCH -[#F59E0B]> TL : Plan returned\nwrong model picked;\nplan too generic
TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Plan accepted

TL -> REV : Phase 1 review
REV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS
end

group Implementation Phase
TL -> CODER : Start implementation
loop 4+ coder loops
CODER --> TL : Handoff / verification claim
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject\nfalse positives,\nmissing handoff,\nquality gate not satisfied
TL -> CODER : Retry with failure evidence
end

TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Code evidence stabilized\nTests, app, API, and Sonar passed

TL -> REV : Phase 2 review
REV -[#F59E0B]> TL : Review artifact malformed / corrupted
TL -[#DC2626]> TL : Red card\nReviewer inconsistency / malformed artifact
TL -> REV : Reviewer rerun
REV -[#F59E0B]> TL : Artifact still malformed

TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Final acceptance blocked\nimplementation evidence stable,\nreview artifact unusable
end

@enduml
